{"tid":1551183,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"9月8 - 美領集會人士請注意","createTime":"2019-09-08T01:20:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T01:54:00.000Z","uid":313463,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b4bdd7d201f1641e861261807e609e494e5f8594","tid":1551183,"uid":313463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:20:41.000Z","msg":"各位手足要注意安全，不論在集會進行還是完結，希望大家可以和平散去，唔好畀對家有藉口施暴，必須保持冷靜，讓法案順利通過，才可制裁相關人士，幫義士討回公道🙏🏻🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n近日網上有位表示自己係知情嘅人士透露，今日嘅集會活動中，會有上頭（唔知係指警方高層，還是中央）會安插30人左右喺活動中搞事，等美國認為示威者係暴徒而唔抵幫，大家可以自行分析。<br />\n<br />\n以下文章大家可以參考一下，未必要同意，但看看無妨，可自行判斷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4vxvnDf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4vxvnDf.png&h=ee4d747e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HAY2YbA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHAY2YbA.png&h=39af49bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98303ef0e0650177337557f8cec4ed4af9f759d6","tid":1551183,"uid":219564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5e5ac294134ffc954919ae8bdde2aa2814542d","tid":1551183,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:26:35.000Z","msg":"集會唔夠，要有請願信<br />\n講出香港市民嘅心聲同希望"},{"pid":"cfe3c534715d82b7fc92e8d7d5ca3a934ada8a57","tid":1551183,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b977b7def68187506e6a6f0b58360a3d3362db8d","tid":1551183,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:33:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bfe744c760791a4fb3b4fc41fba8d6b431e9edc7","tid":1551183,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:54:00.000Z","msg":"未食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}